_sText:
Oh man. I've been stressing on getting this map submitted for weeks. And I've got to say that I'm very happy with it.

Aim_township is an Aim map set in a mountain castle. It features fun close quarters, long range and tactical combat. 

Features:
High dynamic range lighting
A working radar. (non green!) 
A non-intrusive soundscape.
Mountainous 3D skybox.
Custom navigation file.
Sniper tower.
32 player support.
Two easter eggs ;)

Have fun!
